      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:21:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/33/43",
      "text": [
        "٣٣. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): كُنْ سَمَحاً وَلَا تَكُنْ مُبَذِّراً، وَكُنْ مُقَدِّراً وَلَا تَكُنْ مُقَتِّراً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "33. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Be generous but not extravagant; be thrifty but not miserly."
        ]
      }
    }
